Hotmail's delaying Megan's post, but she told me what was in it, so I
get to post with Prowl now. Her post will come in shortly (or longly,
depending on its size).

Pretty much what she did was look behind her, move aside, and hiss (I
think).

::Prowl::

Prowl moves his head back as IR hisses, looking at bit surprised at
her. That wasn't normal behavior! He stretches out to his full height,
growling experimentally at IR.
